snippet.title: Frontend Love
snippet.description:
Starting in February 2018 with Frontend Love & Vue.js Amsterdam we are now responsible for many Conferences in the World: React Live, AngularNL, Vue.js Amsterdam and JSWORLD Conference.

Our ambition was always to give back to the community and create the most awesome experience for attendees from all around the world. JSWORLD Conference is now the largest Javascript Conference in the Netherlands, proudly alongside Vue.js Amsterdam which is the largest Vue Community Conference & Event in the World.

Our upcoming conferences:
➡️ https://vuejs.amsterdam/
➡️ https://jsworldconference.com/
